Hi [~msingh], The patch looks good. Minor suggestion - can you expand the error message a bit? e.g. _No valid proxies left. All NameNode proxies have failed over._

Also in the test case, it may be better to generate a random hostname here:
{code}
            DFS_NAMENODE_RPC_ADDRESS_KEY + "." + singleNS + ".nn1",
        "machine1.foo.bar:9820");
{code}
